\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9395279\charrsid9731846 raspberry}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10315281\charrsid9731846  canes and we had a - a good picking. And w
