Yes, but not quite - he was always occupied so much. He was always having something to do - somebody in trouble - neighbour in trouble or something - always occupied.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11289169 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10315281\charrsid9731846 Did they ever read aloud to you or to each other?
