\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11289169 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10315281\charrsid9731846 Not your grandmother or grandfather?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5462131 VF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10315281\charrsid9731846 
No, no. Me grandmother - she was paralysed at thirty and - she used to - she used to translate lawyers letters from - French and German. But she died when she was thirty. So I never saw her and I got into trouble at school because the Vicar asked u
s if we'd been christened. And of course Norah and I hadn't been christened. Because - dad - didn't believe in christening - he thought you should - you know, be christened when you knew what you were taking on. And this Vicar was terrible cross because w
e
 was at a church school - St Barnabus - and - Norah got up and started screaming and rushed home 'cos he said we wouldn't go to heaven because we weren't christened. And Norah, she got up and - the forms you know that they - you sit on, when one got up th
e
 end one went down. And the - the Vicar - she got up sharp and I stood up - and he went down. But - Norah, she cried and cried - she ran home and she wouldn't go back to that school. So we went to St Katherine's College. But ; that was - that was a - real
l
y terrible for us but was a - we've laughed at it ever since. But - it was a very nice school and it was quite near where we lived. We paid sixpence each for schooling. And then when the board school started dad had the rates in for the educational rating
 
and he refused to pay it because he said he paid for all his children and he wasn't seeing he was going to pay for other peoples so that was - a bit of bone of contention there. He was very - very strict over that. I don't know whether he got summonsed or
 not - I never heard that. Or whether I suppose he paid it. But -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11289169 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10315281\charrsid9731846 Were you taken out visiting neighbours - friends or relations?
