Not a lot. We - you see, you know David Williamson - lives - here - his mother and we used to go quite frequently in
to the - we always went once a year to tea and she had a big spread but - we used to go to our Uncle Alfred's - but - didn't stop there long. These are the younger ones - the elder ones - they did a good bit of - visiting. But younger ones - you - that do
n't count.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11289169 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10315281\charrsid9731846 If you did go visiting who did you go with?
