In some places at that time men felt that they risked losing their job or their home if they voted differently from their employers - do you know if your father felt himself under that kind of pressure?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5462131 VF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10315281\charrsid9731846 No, no, no. No, he was above that - politics.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11289169 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10315281\charrsid9731846 He wasn't a member of a political party?
