 round spouting as I call it, for the Conservative party. He had a van but - it was nothing to do with dad. And that was after he come out of the Salvation Army - I expect he got used to shouting and - out with that th}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4008807\charrsid9731846 en}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10315281\charrsid9731846  he started shouting out about Conservatives.
