Yes. Yes. We went to learn - learn shorthand. Norah and I went to evening but that end
ed with Norah leaving the candle burning in our bedroom and she thought of it all of a sudden and we ran home and the bedroom was alight. So after that we didn't go out of a evening. That stopped us going out of a evening. Marvellous how she kept - how sh
e put that out. All the bed valances and all round the room was all alight and Norah tore upstairs - she remembered what she'd done - she tore upstairs, tore all the things down and stamped on them. Terrible mess. And she'd got plenty of go in her.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11289169 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10315281\charrsid9731846 Do you have any regrets about your education?
