Principally}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10315281\charrsid9731846  singing and - and - hearing one or two of 'em say what they think was right and that sort of thing - kind of teaching us.
