\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10315281\charrsid9731846  while we lived on the Crescent before we moved but I moved with 'em. Wherever they went it seemed 
I was always there because - will, my husband was a very hard worker and he could do the same things as dad in the basket work and so - that's how we went together but - times was very, very hard. There wasn't any work to be had anywhere but -
\par 
