I never did because I suffered with bronchial asthma, you see, so I never - me sister used to - Norah used to and Will used to go out together because I couldn't so - I had to stop at home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11289169 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10315281\charrsid9731846 Did you make any new friends - boys or girls - at this time?
