Yes, well - yes. At that time we - we was - friendly with all of them just around handy. I could name several of them but - I can't think of them. David Williamson was one and he's - he's stopped with me right 'til now
. He's - he lives in West Mersea but - I never took any active part in the politics not going out of a evening but that was my views.
